\end_inset

, entonces 
\begin_inset Formula $f(A)=(f^{-1})^{-1}(A)=g^{-1}(A)\in{\cal T}'$
\end_inset

.
 Recíprocamente, si 
\begin_inset Formula $f(A)\in{\cal T}'$
\end_inset

 entonces 
\begin_inset Formula $f^{-1}(f(A))=A\in{\cal T}$
\end_inset

.
