, si 
\begin_inset Formula $f(A)\in{\cal T}'$
\end_inset

 entonces 
\begin_inset Formula $f^{-1}(f(A))=A\in{\cal T}$
\end_inset

.
 Para ver que 
\begin_inset Formula $g:=f^{-1}$
\end_inset

 es continua, dado 
\begin_inset Formula $A\subseteq X$
